{"tid":1647260,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我原諒香港警察","createTime":"2019-10-11T16:21:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T16:51:03.000Z","uid":284461,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"607a8f5ff09398c79badfe88f9da8d75a5e7e8b1","tid":1647260,"uid":284461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T16:21:31.000Z","msg":"只會喺一個情況下發生<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就係你地武裝對抗 做叛軍！</span></span><br />\n現今香港喺國際上仲未算係武裝衝突 只係騷亂<br />\n如果有警察做武裝對抗 就一定會引起國際調停 唔再係純粹冇意義嘅關注<br />\n到時就有籌碼令政府跪低<br />\n一路以來都有咁多警察扮家長車嘅情報<br />\n代表入邊仲有好多係仲有良知嘅警察<br />\n呢個係你哋嘅最後機會<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">去做一個人 唔使再做狗</span><br />\n如果咁樣叫埋你去做 你都要繼續扮訓<br />\n咁你以後都只會係行咇都俾人吐口水嘅<span style=\"color: blue;\">過街老鼠</span><br />\nMon post 狗 唔關你事呀 繼續用警察官方ig𥄫女啦"},{"pid":"65128a07e70329c6c0bc6057d96df483934794ea","tid":1647260,"uid":284461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T16:21:56.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"678e35c88e3a7bc02fcdb970ef6eeabaa8931961","tid":1647260,"uid":284461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T16:22:07.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"6d5a05034d45b657f70ef5d0086beb1791ae4a68","tid":1647260,"uid":284461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T16:22:17.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"c704d6b0d8f4047523714428f76606a6af104b11","tid":1647260,"uid":284461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T16:22:27.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"58e4bf2c439b55f6bd4eed5b897904ec3a90d453","tid":1647260,"uid":284461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T16:22:37.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"a125365f4667e1a1028e75f9536bdadd307e6eb7","tid":1647260,"uid":284461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T16:22:48.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"3c233409d5a2219a770e9bc5598ce9705527b9d1","tid":1647260,"uid":284461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T16:22:58.0